### 📋 沙盒创建流程（v3.0）

```bash
# 1. 创建沙盒目录
mkdir -p /tmp/openclaw-sandbox-3.8/.openclaw/{extensions,agents,logs}

# 2. 创建独立配置（不修改生产！）
cat > /tmp/openclaw-sandbox-3.8/.openclaw/openclaw.json << 'EOF'
{
  "gateway": {"port": 18800, "bind": "loopback"},
  "plugins": {"allow": []}
}
EOF

# 3. 验证配置（关键！）
OPENCLAW_HOME=/tmp/openclaw-sandbox-3.8/.openclaw openclaw config validate

# 4. 备份配置（关键！）
cp /tmp/openclaw-sandbox-3.8/.openclaw/openclaw.json \
   /tmp/openclaw-sandbox-3.8/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak

# 5. 启动沙盒
export OPENCLAW_HOME=/tmp/openclaw-sandbox-3.8/.openclaw
nohup openclaw gateway run --port 18800 > logs/gateway.log 2>&1 &

# 6. 清理环境变量（关键！）
unset OPENCLAW_HOME
```

